==PURPOSE==
Move JSX-bearing Tam Luxury source files from .ts to .na, then enable Vite transitional loader to treat .na as TSX.
This intentionally does not restore .tsx. It pushes the Tam Luxury source toward Nauion extension first, then fixes runtime/build compatibility.
==END==

